headline: EQT Reports Third Quarter 2025 Results
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE: EQT) today announced financial and operational results for the third quarter of 2025.

headline: ONCOR TO RELEASE THIRD QUARTER 2025 RESULTS NOVEMBER 5
summary: Oncor Electric Delivery Company LLC ("Oncor") plans to release its third quarter 2025 results on November 5, prior to Sempra's (NYSE: SRE) third quarter 2025 results conference call. Oncor's earnings release will be available on Oncor's website, oncor.com.
